            Nicho's Quality Wears provides the best prices on footwear, sneakers, shirts, and bags. High quality that fits your budget perfectly.
          </p>
          <div className="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
            <a 
              href="#shop" 
              className="inline-block bg-yellow-500 text-green-950 font-bold px-10 py-4 rounded-full shadow-lg hover:bg-yellow-400 transition transform hover:-translate-y-1"
            >
              Shop Latest Stock
            </a>
            <div className="flex items-center justify-center gap-2 text-yellow-400 font-medium bg-green-800/50 px-6 py-4 rounded-full border border-green-700">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" strokeWidth="2" strokeLinecap="round" strokeLinejoin="round"><path d="M20 10c0 6-8 12-8 12s-8-6-8-12a8 8 0 0 1 16 0Z"/><circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"/></svg>
              <span>Based in Tadi</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </header>

